<A>__{whooom! fait's flying. seventy plus. down streets, sidewalks, squeezing through places police cars can't. over, under, around, through doesn't matter. the atv's fast, strong and maneuverable. one problem: so is the moto cross bike. the guy's right on fait's ass. matching move with move. overhead, police choppers follow fait's every move. while on the ground other police vehicles move to block his path. but whenever fait meets a roadblock, he somehow finds an escape. at one point, he uses an outdoor escalator. at another point he blasts through the hotel bonaventure. this'll be a news highlight for days to come.}
